{
  "stem": "7016.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I drank so much water, and then I said to myself, I go to the electric wires because [CRYING] you was all sick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went, and I wanted-- and you touched-- the whole camp was with electric wires.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they told us right away, if you go to those wires, you get electrified and die right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was thinking, this is going to be the best for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the top was a-- a-- a tower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, around the camp was towers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- it was not a gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think this was regular soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how I went to the-- to the electric wire was a hill like a little river.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to cross to go, and I want to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that-- and that-- it's so painful-- and that soldier, the Germans start to holler me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I should-- I should go away because he gonna shoot at me, would want one to kill me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I said to him, I want to be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't want to live no more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm sick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not gonna live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then he start to shoot, not on me, on the air.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I should get scared, not to go close, and he start to call a kapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was in the night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a kapo outside, which there was looking around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He start to call her, and she came to me, and she start to holler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I-- I told her that I'm not gonna live, and I cannot live, that I'm so sick.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE], and you-- you're so sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You have typhus.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he said, he should ask me which block I'm in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She take me back to the block.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
